34 SUMMARY
3355 This amendment replaces the bill's ongoing General Fund appropriations with one-time
3366 General Fund appropriations of $1,000,000 in each of fiscal years 2025-26 and 2026-27 to
3377 the Maine State Housing Authority for the new Housing Stability Support Program
3388 established to provide assistance to eligible renters to prevent eviction. The amendment
3399 also includes a one-time adjustment in each of fiscal years 2025-26 and 2026-27 in the
4400 share of the real estate transfer tax retained by counties from 10% to 9.2%. The amendment
Page 2 - 132LR1976(04)
